Package com.atmecs.falcon.automation.rest.endpoint

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IRequestBuilder  
    IRestService
    IRestService interface is for declaring a method called getResponse() which takes 2 arguments JSONObject is for URI and Map is for header info
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DeleteHttpVerb
    DeleteHttpVerb class implements DELETE (along with HEAD) requests It deletes the record form the database based on URI
    GetHttpVerb
    GetHttpVerb class implements GET (along with HEAD) requests which is used only to read data and not change it.
    PostHttpVerb
    PostHttpVerb class implements POST (along with HEAD) requests It creates the record into the database based on URI
    PutHttpVerb
    PutHttpVerb class implements PUT (along with HEAD) requests It updates the record information (which provides as request parameters) in the database based on URI
    RequestBuilder  
    ResponseOptions  
    ResponseService  
    RestServiceImpl
    RestServiceImpl class provides all the service objects depends on the method type 1.
